(155, 'Can I use any coolant for my AC, or should I stick to a specific type?', 'We recommend using the coolant specified by your AC manufacturer for optimal performance and efficiency.', 37, 1, '2024-02-01 03:45:44', '2024-02-01 03:45:44'),
(156, 'What does an AC tune-up include?', 'Our comprehensive service covers cleaning, lubricating, checking refrigerant levels, and ensuring all components are in top condition.', 36, 1, '2024-02-01 06:28:24', '2024-02-01 06:28:24'),
(157, 'Is a tune-up necessary for newly installed AC units?', 'Absolutely! Regular maintenance, even for new units, ensures optimal performance, prevents issues, and extends the lifespan of your system.', 36, 1, '2024-02-01 06:28:41', '2024-02-01 06:28:41'),
(158, 'Do I need to provide cleaning supplies and equipment?', 'No need! Our professionals bring all the necessary supplies and equipment for a comprehensive deep cleaning.', 35, 1, '2024-02-01 06:29:35', '2024-02-01 06:29:35'),
(159, 'Are your cleaning products safe for pets and children?', 'Yes, our cleaning products are selected for their effectiveness and safety, making them suitable for households with pets and children.', 35, 1, '2024-02-01 06:29:52', '2024-02-01 06:29:52'),
(160, 'What materials are commonly used for door casing and trim?', 'Wood, MDF, and PVC are popular choices for durability and aesthetic appeal.', 34, 1, '2024-02-01 06:30:46', '2024-02-01 06:30:46'),
(161, 'Is it necessary to remove the old trim before installing new casing?', 'Yes, removing old trim ensures a clean installation and a polished final look.', 34, 1, '2024-02-01 06:31:19', '2024-02-01 06:31:19'),
(162, 's a transmission flush necessary?', 'Regular fluid changes are essential, but a flush may not always be necessary. Consult with our experts to determine the best maintenance for your vehicle.', 33, 1, '2024-02-01 06:32:20', '2024-02-01 06:32:20'),
(163, 'Can I drive with a slipping transmission?', 'Driving with a slipping transmission can cause further damage. It\'s advisable to have it inspected and repaired promptly.', 33, 1, '2024-02-01 06:32:43', '2024-02-01 06:32:43'),
(164, 'Can you remove stubborn stains from my car seats?', 'Yes, our specialized cleaning techniques can effectively remove most stains, rejuvenating your car seats.', 32, 1, '2024-02-01 06:33:20', '2024-02-01 06:33:20'),
(165, 'Do I need to remove personal items before the cleaning session?', 'It\'s advisable to remove personal items for a thorough cleaning, but our team can work around them if needed.', 32, 1, '2024-02-01 06:33:39', '2024-02-01 06:33:39'),
(166, 'Can I drive my car if the check engine light is on?', 'It\'s not recommended. Continuing to drive with the check engine light on may worsen the issue. Schedule diagnostics promptly.', 31, 1, '2024-02-01 06:34:29', '2024-02-01 06:34:29'),
(167, 'Is engine diagnostics the same as a regular car inspection?', 'No, engine diagnostics specifically focuses on identifying and resolving issues related to the engine\'s performance.', 31, 1, '2024-02-01 06:34:46', '2024-02-01 06:34:46'),
(168, 'Can outdoor lights be automated or controlled remotely?', 'Yes, we offer smart solutions for automation and remote control of your outdoor lighting.', 30, 1, '2024-02-01 07:11:17', '2024-02-01 07:11:17'),
(169, 'Are energy-efficient options available for outdoor lighting?', 'Absolutely! Choose LED fixtures and smart controls for energy savings and eco-friendly options.', 30, 1, '2024-02-01 07:11:33', '2024-02-01 07:11:33'),
(170, 'Can you install smart lighting systems during the service?', 'Certainly! Our electricians are equipped to install and set up smart lighting systems for your convenience.', 29, 1, '2024-02-01 07:12:28', '2024-02-01 07:12:28'),
(171, 'Can I choose my own light fixtures for installation?', 'Absolutely! You can choose your preferred fixtures, and our electricians will handle the installation.', 29, 1, '2024-02-01 07:12:48', '2024-02-01 07:12:48'),
(172, 'What causes wiring issues in a home?', 'Wiring issues can stem from aging, rodents, or faulty installations. Regular inspections help identify and address potential problems.', 28, 1, '2024-02-01 07:13:26', '2024-02-01 07:13:26'),
(173, 'How long does a typical wiring repair take?', 'The duration depends on the extent of the issue. Simple repairs may take a few hours, while more complex ones could span a day.', 28, 1, '2024-02-01 07:13:44', '2024-02-01 07:13:44'),
(174, 'Can I request gluten-free pasta for my dish?', 'Certainly! We accommodate dietary preferences, including gluten-free options.', 27, 1, '2024-02-01 07:14:29', '2024-02-01 07:14:29'),
(175, 'Are your ingredients sourced from Italy for an authentic taste?', 'While some ingredients are imported, we prioritize freshness and quality for an authentic Italian experience.', 27, 1, '2024-02-01 07:14:49', '2024-02-01 07:14:49'),
(176, 'What\'s the difference between Cantonese and Szechuan cuisine?', 'Cantonese is known for freshness, while Szechuan is spicy and bold. Explore both for a diverse culinary experience.', 26, 1, '2024-02-01 07:15:29', '2024-02-01 07:15:29'),
(177, 'How can I reheat Chinese takeout for the best flavor?', 'Reheat in a pan or oven for crispy textures. Avoid using the microwave to maintain the dish\'s original flavor and texture.', 26, 1, '2024-02-01 07:15:57', '2024-02-01 07:15:57'),
(178, 'Can the chef accommodate dietary restrictions and allergies?', 'Absolutely! We work closely with clients to accommodate dietary restrictions and ensure a safe and enjoyable dining experience.', 25, 1, '2024-02-01 07:16:54', '2024-02-01 07:16:54'),
(179, 'Can I request a customized menu for my event from the Authentic Mexican Chef?', 'Absolutely! Our chef specializes in creating personalized menus tailored to your preferences and event theme.', 25, 1, '2024-02-01 07:17:08', '2024-02-01 07:17:08'),
(180, 'What is included in the family-style dinner package?', 'The package includes menu planning, ingredient sourcing, preparation, and cleanup, ensuring a hassle-free and delightful dining experience for your family.', 24, 1, '2024-02-01 07:18:22', '2024-02-01 07:18:22'),
(181, 'Are ingredients sourced responsibly and locally?', 'Yes, we prioritize quality. Our chefs use fresh, locally sourced ingredients for a delectable and sustainable dining experience.', 24, 1, '2024-02-01 07:18:37', '2024-02-01 07:18:37'),
(182, 'Are the ingredients sourced fresh?', 'Absolutely! We prioritize using fresh, high-quality ingredients to create delicious and nutritious meals for you.', 23, 1, '2024-02-01 07:19:19', '2024-02-01 07:19:19'),
(183, 'Can I request specific cuisines or styles of cooking?', 'Certainly! Our cooks are versatile and can prepare meals in various cuisines or styles based on your preferences.', 23, 1, '2024-02-01 07:19:33', '2024-02-01 07:19:33'),
(184, 'Can I leave my curtains hanging during the cleaning process?', 'Yes, our professional team performs on-site cleaning without the need for curtain removal.', 21, 1, '2024-02-01 07:20:50', '2024-02-01 07:20:50'),
(185, 'What types of curtains do you clean?', 'We clean all types, including drapes, sheers, and fabric blinds, ensuring a thorough and gentle process.', 21, 1, '2024-02-01 07:21:10', '2024-02-01 07:21:10'),
(186, 'How long does the carpet drying process take?', 'Drying times vary but typically range from 4 to 6 hours. Ventilation and weather conditions can impact drying.', 20, 1, '2024-02-01 07:22:03', '2024-02-01 07:22:03'),
(187, 'Is there a specific carpet cleaning method you recommend?', 'We tailor our approach to your carpet\'s needs, utilizing steam cleaning, dry cleaning, or other methods for optimal results.', 20, 1, '2024-02-01 07:22:17', '2024-02-01 07:22:17'),
(188, 'Can you clean hard-to-reach areas, like high ceilings or crown moldings?', 'Absolutely! Our team is equipped to handle hard-to-reach areas using safe and effective cleaning methods.', 19, 1, '2024-02-01 07:23:09', '2024-02-01 07:23:09'),
(189, 'Will Ceiling and Wall Cleaning remove stains or discoloration?', 'In most cases, our cleaning process can significantly improve the appearance of stains and discoloration. However, complete removal depends on the nature of the stain.', 19, 1, '2024-02-01 07:23:22', '2024-02-01 07:23:22'),
(190, 'What areas of the house are covered in a full house cleaning?', 'Our service covers all essential areas, including bedrooms, bathrooms, kitchen, living spaces, and common areas, providing a comprehensive clean.', 18, 1, '2024-02-01 07:24:08', '2024-02-01 07:24:08'),
(191, 'Do I need to provide cleaning supplies?', 'No need! Our professional cleaners bring their own supplies, ensuring a thorough and effective cleaning.', 18, 1, '2024-02-01 07:24:24', '2024-02-01 07:24:24'),
(192, 'Can you install beams and columns for both residential and commercial spaces?', 'Absolutely! Our skilled team is experienced in installations for both residential and commercial properties.', 17, 1, '2024-02-01 07:25:12', '2024-02-01 07:25:12'),
(193, 'What is the average lifespan of installed beams and columns?', 'The lifespan depends on factors like material and environmental conditions. We use durable materials for long-lasting results.', 17, 1, '2024-02-01 07:25:24', '2024-02-01 07:25:24'),
(194, 'How often should cabinets be refinished for optimal maintenance?', 'Refinishing is typically done every 5-10 years, depending on wear and tear and personal preference.', 16, 1, '2024-02-01 07:26:04', '2024-02-01 07:26:04'),
(195, 'Is it possible to fix a cabinet that\'s been damaged or has loose hinges?', 'Yes, our experts can address cabinet damage, including fixing loose hinges and repairing other issues.', 16, 1, '2024-02-01 07:26:18', '2024-02-01 07:26:18'),
(196, 'Can I choose a different stain or finish for my chair?', 'Certainly! Customize your chair\'s look by choosing from our range of stains and finishes.', 15, 1, '2024-02-01 07:26:59', '2024-02-01 07:26:59'),
(197, 'Will the restoration remove scratches and dents?', 'Yes, our restoration process includes repairing scratches, dents, and other visible damages for a like-new appearance.', 15, 1, '2024-02-01 07:27:13', '2024-02-01 07:27:13'),
(198, 'Can I rotate and balance my tires at home?', 'It\'s a specialized process best done by professionals using the right equipment for accurate results.', 14, 1, '2024-02-01 07:28:36', '2024-02-01 07:28:36');
INSERT INTO `service_faqs` (`id`, `title`, `description`, `service_id`, `status`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(199, 'What\'s the difference between tire rotation and balancing?', 'Rotation ensures even wear on all tires, while balancing optimizes weight distribution, preventing vibrations.', 14, 1, '2024-02-01 07:28:45', '2024-02-01 07:28:45'),
(200, 'Do you check other fluids during an oil change?', 'Absolutely! Our service includes a thorough check of essential fluids like coolant, brake fluid, and transmission fluid.', 13, 1, '2024-02-01 07:29:29', '2024-02-01 07:29:29'),
(201, 'What signs indicate my car needs an oil change?', 'Look out for warning lights, dark or gritty oil, and engine noise – these may indicate it\'s time for a change.', 13, 1, '2024-02-01 07:29:45', '2024-02-01 07:29:45'),
(202, 'What is included in the installation service?', 'Our service includes mounting the unit securely, sealing gaps, and testing for proper functionality.', 12, 1, '2024-02-01 07:30:31', '2024-02-01 07:30:31'),
(203, 'Is there anything I need to prepare before the installation?', 'Ensure the designated window is accessible and clear. We\'ll take care of the rest.', 12, 1, '2024-02-01 07:30:47', '2024-02-01 07:30:47'),
(204, 'Can I install a split AC in any room?', 'Yes, as long as the room size is compatible with the AC capacity. Consult with our experts for personalized recommendations.', 11, 1, '2024-02-01 07:31:26', '2024-02-01 07:31:26'),
(205, 'Can I relocate a split AC unit after installation?', 'It\'s possible, but it\'s recommended to consult with our technicians to assess feasibility and ensure proper relocation.', 11, 1, '2024-02-01 07:31:38', '2024-02-01 07:31:38');
INSERT INTO `service_packages` (`id`, `provider_id`, `category_id`, `subcategory_id`, `name`, `description`, `price`, `start_at`, `end_at`, `status`, `is_featured`, `package_type`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(1, 4, 14, 25, 'Cắt và nhuộm tóc', 'Nâng tầm diện mạo của bạn với Gói kết hợp cắt tóc và nhuộm tóc của chúng tôi. Các nhà tạo mẫu tóc lành nghề của chúng tôi tạo ra những kiểu tóc cá nhân hóa và thêm màu sắc rực rỡ, tạo nên sự thay đổi hài hòa phù hợp với phong cách và cá tính của bạn, tất cả trong một gói tiện lợi. ??', 50, '2023-09-09 00:00:00', '2026-09-30 00:00:00', 0, 0, 'single', '2023-09-09 05:45:30', '2025-04-18 14:44:43'),
(3, 4, 18, 36, 'Khung tranh', 'Nâng tầm nội thất của bạn với gói kết hợp Thiết kế khung nghệ thuật và Tranh nhiều khung của chúng tôi! Các nghệ sĩ tài năng của chúng tôi sẽ tạo ra những bức tranh tuyệt đẹp theo phong cách của bạn, trong khi các nhà thiết kế khung của chúng tôi sẽ chế tạo các khung tùy chỉnh để bổ sung cho tác phẩm nghệ thuật của bạn. Biến không gian của bạn thành một tác phẩm nghệ thuật với sự kết hợp hoàn hảo này. ??‍??️?', 55, '2023-10-06 12:00:00', '2026-12-31 12:00:00', 0, 0, 'single', '2023-10-05 23:53:26', '2025-04-18 14:44:43'),
(4, 4, 19, 38, 'Gói dịch vụ giặt ủi', 'Trải nghiệm sự sang trọng trong từng sợi vải với Gói dịch vụ giặt ủi của chúng tôi! Gói này kết hợp giữa dịch vụ chăm sóc lụa và trang phục thiết kế tỉ mỉ ??? với dịch vụ giặt váy dạ hội và trang phục trang trọng tinh tươm. Chúng tôi đảm bảo những loại vải mỏng manh nhất và trang phục đặc biệt của bạn được chăm sóc chu đáo, giúp bạn trông và cảm thấy tuyệt vời trong mọi dịp. ???', 38, NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 'single', '2023-10-06 00:05:09', '2025-04-18 14:44:42'),
(5, 17, NULL, NULL, 'GreenGuard và CommercialShield: Người bảo vệ không gian của bạn', 'GreenGuard và CommercialShield cung cấp các giải pháp an ninh toàn diện cho cả không gian xanh và tòa nhà thương mại của bạn. Với các dịch vụ chuyên gia của chúng tôi, tài sản của bạn được bảo vệ cả bên trong và bên ngoài, đảm bảo an toàn và sự an tâm.', 480000, NULL, NULL, 1, 0, 'multiple', '2023-10-06 00:19:45', '2025-04-18 14:44:35'),
(6, 4, NULL, NULL, 'Thợ mộc và vệ sinh', 'Nâng cấp không gian của bạn với dịch vụ mộc và vệ sinh! Những người thợ mộc lành nghề của chúng tôi sẽ biến tầm nhìn của bạn thành hiện thực, trong khi các chuyên gia vệ sinh của chúng tôi đảm bảo một môi trường sạch sẽ và an toàn. Đây là sự kết hợp hoàn hảo giữa tay nghề thủ công và sự sạch sẽ cho ngôi nhà hoặc văn phòng của bạn. ⚒️?', 1200000, NULL, NULL, 1, 0, 'multiple', '2023-10-06 00:25:51', '2025-04-18 14:44:18'),
(7, 4, NULL, NULL, 'Bộ bảo vệ nhà thông minh', 'Tăng cường sự an toàn và hiệu quả cho ngôi nhà của bạn với Bộ bảo vệ nhà thông minh của chúng tôi. Gói toàn diện này bao gồm Lắp đặt hệ thống báo động, Lắp đặt đèn thông minh, Tích hợp thiết bị thông minh, Sửa chữa rò rỉ và Làm sạch đường ống thoát nước. Tận hưởng sự an tâm và tiện lợi, tất cả trong một gói. ???‍??', 860000, NULL, NULL, 1, 0, 'multiple', '2023-10-06 00:35:25', '2025-04-18 14:43:44'),
(8, 4, 22, 9, 'Sự kết hợp ẩm thực toàn cầu', 'Khám phá những món ăn ngon đa dạng với dịch vụ kết hợp Đầu bếp Mexico chính hiệu ???, Đồ ăn Trung Hoa ?? và Đầu bếp Ý ?? của chúng tôi. Thưởng thức thế giới hương vị, tất cả trong một gói. ??', 1000000, NULL, NULL, 1, 0, 'single', '2023-10-06 01:22:05', '2025-04-18 14:43:12');
